{"id": 4966, "title": "Ticket #4966: Fix MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default value", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe default value for config param MAX_JOBS_RUNNING is calculated based on the amount of physical memory on the machine. The calculation done in the schedd is an order of magnitude too large. Additionally, the calculation can overflow 32-bit signed integers and result in a negative value. The default expression in the param table is overly complex. For both, we can use the number of megabytes of memory as the limit.\n\n<p>Thanks to Ben Plotnick for notifying us about this problem.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2015-Mar-31 15:23:32 by tlmiller:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>Code Review</strong>\n\n<p>Looks good.</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Apr-01 16:32</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/4f9e469b1808e7d327d5e1aae1073d96a56804f0\">[44494]</a></span>: minor 8.2.8 version history item edit <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=4966\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4966'); return false;\" title=\"Fix MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default value\">#4966</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Mar-31 15:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/49137b0ee6fefeb0eb2897ac327c57492c356a02\">[44479]</a></span>: Docs for MAX_JOB_RUNNING default value fixes. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=4966\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4966'); return false;\" title=\"Fix MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default value\">#4966</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Mar-31 15:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/93057eedb6ee77f548fe21078a2ae71beecc5e4e\">[44477]</a></span>: Fix MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default value in schedd. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=4966\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4966'); return false;\" title=\"Fix MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default value\">#4966</a></span> The default value calculated by the schedd is 10 times too large.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Mar-31 15:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/2c2f628dd7993d571aad6c1d707fc3f0e95eb175\">[44478]</a></span>: Simplify MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default in the param table. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=4966\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4966'); return false;\" title=\"Fix MAX_JOBS_RUNNING default value\">#4966</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2015-Mar-31 16:02", "status": "resolved", "created": "2015-Mar-31 14:39", "fixed_version": "2015-Mar-31 14:39", "broken_version": "v080200", "priority": "3", "subsystem": "DaemonsSubmitNode", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "", "customer_group": "users", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}